Pseudo code for "Monthly sales Tax" program

PROMPT user "What was your total sales this month? "
SAVE input as variable sales_total
CALCULATE the county_tax(0.25) TIMES sales_total
SAVE value as county_sales_tax
CALCULATE the state_tax(0.5) TIMES sales_total
SAVE value as state_sales_tax
CALCULATE the SUM of state_sales_tax AND county_sales_tax
SAVE value as total_sales_tax
Then will DISPLAY:
county_sales_tax
state_sales_tax
total_sales_tax
to the user.
END